        Xavier Becerra, Attorney General, Kristen Ramirez and Daniel Hilton, Deputy

Attorneys General, for Plaintiff and Respondent.

(Pen. Code,1 § 211; counts 2, 3, 4, and 24). For three of these counts (counts 2, 3, and 4),
